'''Meet me at the Crossroads''' is a side [[Quests|quest]] in [[Sal|Sal's]] campaign with a focus on [[Battle]].

== Description ==
Join a [[Spree]] member at an ambush point and help choose robbery targets. You'll get a cut of the loot, if you both survive.

Difficulty: ★★☆☆☆

== Rewards ==

* Shills that you got out of robbing
* Restoration - Restore 20 health or 10 resolve

